g.title: Sheet.33
g.desc: Off1 : Any command which causes the OnOff attribute to be set...
g.text: Off1 : Any command which causes the OnOff attribute to be set to FALSE, e.g. Off, Toggle or OffWithEffect.On2 : Any command which causes the OnOff attribute to be set to TRUE, e.g. On, Toggle or OnWithRecallGlobalScene.
